1
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,280
Why has Xu Nan come?

2
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:11,640
Matriarch Lü and the Madam of the Wang Family are distant kin

3
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:14,640
The Wang Family had to send someone for Matriarch Lü's funeral

4
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,200
Wang Shengchang has vanished without a trace

5
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,400
Things with your sister-in-law have gone nowhere

6
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,520
You're in no hurry at all

7
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,560
Why not take this chance

8
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,440
and quickly leave the Wang Family with her

9
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,880
I know her temperament

10
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:31,320
No one can stop what she wants to do

11
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,360
All right, all right

12
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:41,080
It is our honor to receive the Fifth Concubine of the Wang Family

13
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,680
A true honor indeed

14
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,360
Third Madam, my condolences

15
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,880
My master had to go out on business

16
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:50,960
So I have come on behalf of the Wang Family to mourn your matriarch

17
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,600
They are truly so alike

18
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:55,800
The Fifth and Fourth Concubines truly are twin flowers

19
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:02,760
Forgive me, my loose tongue spoke out of turn again

20
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,960
It's no matter

21
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,760
I heard the Eldest Young Master has fallen ill as well

22
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:11,680
I specially brought fine medicinal herbs to visit him

23
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,320
Our Zhao Family is a lineage of perfumers and herbalists

24
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,600
I know a little medicine

25
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,600
Then many thanks indeed

26
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,120
In that case

27
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,920
take the Fifth Concubine to see the Eldest Young Master

28
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,240
Yes, this way please

29
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,360
I can go in by myself

30
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,840
Go attend to your work

31
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,520
Yes

32
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,400
It's you

33
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,480
A ghost!

34
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,120
A ghost!

35
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,920
Fox paw prints and fur

36
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,120
Could the curse of the fox spirit be real?

37
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,600
This...

38
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,080
What use is making a rubbing of these prints?

39
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:21,360
An adult has 206 bones

40
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:23,160
A child has a few more

41
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:26,000
About 217 to 218

42
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,800
From the bones' size and age

43
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,680
you can tell how old the person was

44
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,280
It is the same with animals

45
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,960
Then what have you learned from these prints?

46
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,520
Nothing for now

47
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,280
I am not a ghost

48
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,240
The one who died was my elder sister

49
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,480
Zhao Xujun

50
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,080
I was discourteous

51
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:53,400
Your reaction just now made it seem you feared her greatly

52
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,240
I did not

53
00:03:57,600 --> 00:04:00,160
Afraid my sister's vengeful spirit would come for your life?

54
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,560
No

55
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,120
She once came to the Lü family for help

56
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,920
You and Matriarch Lü drove her out

57
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,400
What secret are you hiding for the Wang Family?

58
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:13,440
I...

59
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,360
Speak

60
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,040
It was not me

61
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,160
It was Lü Quan

62
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:27,000
Eldest Young Master, save me! Your sister sought help from Lü Quan

63
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,440
It was not me

64
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,680
He and the matriarch were the ones who abandoned your sister. Save me!

65
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,480
Eldest Young Master, it was them, them!

66
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,720
It had nothing to do with me!

67
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,240
They did it all

68
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,360
They did it

69
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,120
Do not come for me

70
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:25,240
I have truly never heard of such a strange thing

71
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,280
When he just went mad

72
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,400
a strange, eerie odor came off him

73
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,240
As if he had been poisoned by some rare toxin

74
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,000
What is it?

75
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,320
It is actually a fox spirit

76
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,480
Eldest Young Master

77
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,440
The Lü family has met with misfortune

78
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,720
To prevent more mishaps

79
00:06:57,200 --> 00:07:00,080
We earnestly ask Mr. Zheng to hold the bone-collecting ritual at once

80
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,640
This is my first time collecting bones for an animal

81
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,640
Though it is not human

82
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:10,800
it was once still a living creature

83
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:14,760
and should be treated seriously

84
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,280
Break ground

85
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,120
Open the coffin

86
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,400
These fox bones are hard in texture

87
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,000
They have not weathered away

88
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,960
It has been dead no more than one year

89
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:10,080
This is no fox spirit the Lü ancestors killed by mistake a hundred years ago
